              <h3 class="text-theme-colored mt-0 pt-5">Volunteer Opportunities</h3>
              <hr>
              <p class="mb-20">Volunteering is contribution of time, effort and talent to a need, cause or mission without financial gain. Volunteering is all about you being able to contribute some of your own time to help people in our communities.</p>
                            <p class="mb-20">Volunteers are idealistically motivated persons who want to devote some portion of their lives to serving others. To do volunteer services for the organization depends upon the personal desire of the individual. Individual are actively participating for voluntary services for their own satisfaction.</p>
                              <p class="mb-20">ODH Foundation believes that sustainable change, the citizens of the society have to be proactively involved in the process of development.ODH Foundation giving opportunities for volunteers like Students, Businessman, work professional, Home maker, Retired individual, Ex- Service man and even currently working young people who would like to serve their free time as a part of volunteering. It is purely an unpaid service from the volunteers. The volunteers can spend their time with ODH Foundation in giving trainings, sessions to children, fundraising opportunities, operation, teaching and can participate in community work etc. ODH Foundation will not provide any stipend/salary to volunteers. Volunteers are the backbone of every organization. They not only carry the organization’s ideals within them, but also spread the message far and beyond, sensitizing the society towards the cause.  We expect volunteers behave in a professional and responsible manner during their time of their work with us in which they would be given a specific task of their interest which they can perform.</p>

            </div>
            
           
            <div id="section-four" class="mb-50">
             
              <h5 class="text-theme-colored mt-0 pt-5">ODH Foundation has many Online/Offline Volunteer Opportunities:</h5>
              <p class="mb-20">Many times, you feel the need to work for a good cause but somehow your busy routine holds you back and then when you get time to look back, you try to convince yourself by saying that If I had time, I would have contributed a little bit to the society.But believe us if you have the guts and passion to support a cause then you too can bring smile on the face of the underprivileged children of the society and can help for women empowerment and to make the environment protected and pollution free all this without it being any demanding on your daily routine.<br />
                 
</p>
             
            </div>
