              <h5 class="text-theme-colored mt-0 pt-5">Operations Intern Opportunities for Volunteers</h5>
              <p class="mb-20">We are seeking a passionate and driven individual who shares our values and is committed to making a difference. If you are interested in joining our ODH Foundation team and making a difference, we encourage you to apply for this exciting opportunity. Selected intern's day-to-day responsibilities include the below task: </p>
