              <h5 class="text-theme-colored mt-0 pt-5">Graphic Designer Opportunities for Volunteers</h5>
              <p class="mb-20">Are you a person who is artistically creative? We are looking for one such person who is interested in depicting our story. We are active in the core areas of education, health, sustainable livelihoods, skill development and women economic empowerment, innovative healthcare awareness program, empower underprivileged children and we are in need of a compelling word artist who can research and write content for us. The Graphic Designer would be working with the team to articulate our thoughts into compelling creatives for various platforms such as social media, website, presentations etc. We are a team of collaborators who come from different backgrounds. The candidate must have proven designing skills for social media. Join ODH Foundation for a fun and memorable learning experience.</p>
             
            </div>
